data.description: Welcome to your dream home in this exclusive 55+ community! This impeccable ranch-style residence boasts 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, a flex room with elegant glass French doors for privacy and a sun room. With 1950 square feet of luxury living, the crown molding and tray ceilings elevate the design. Marvel at the beautifully selected quartz countertops and extended kitchen island in this chef's dream kitchen, complete with Kitchen Aid stainless steel appliances.and an expansive walk-in pantry, The ''Super Shower'' in the en-suite bathroom is a zero-entry tiled oasis complete with a bench and the luxury finishes include modern designed rectangular sinks. This barely-lived-in gem features tray ceilings, natural light, and a tastefully chosen color palette throughout the open floor planThe second bedroom to the front of the house provides privacy and tranquility for both you and your guests. Your dedicated laundry room is complete with a wash basin for pre-soaking or other needs. There is also a convenient drop zone area which is perfect for keeping your items in one space after entering your home from the garage or the front door entry.  Enhanced by an extended front entry hallway, the home includes a 2-car finished garage with a 4-foot extension for ample storage options. The screened-in porch, and cement pad offer both comfort and style for entertaining friends or spending lazy days and evenings at home. The lot is enclosed with aluminum fencing so you are able to enjoy the serene surroundings on a quiet street with a berm view. Take advantage of resort-style amenities in the ideal location, close to all of the wonderful shops and fabulous local restaurants plus convenient highway access. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the epitome of 55+ living in this meticulously crafted and thoughtfully designed home. Whether you have an active lifestyle or prefer to be at home, this community is the perfect choice for you! Enjoy the resort style pool, sauna, pickle ball courts, tennis courts or even one of the monthly events such as a live concert-you will surely elevate your lifestyle residing in this well maintained and friendly community. You may even decide to invest in a golf cart as this community thrives on this laid back and fancy free lifestyle.   Upcoming amenities to include an Amphitheatre, dog park and more!!  Please check out the additional documents to include the most sought after plan known as the Palmary. There is also a detailed list of all of the recent upgrades. The Seller has capped off the gas for the gas stove/oven but it can easily be converted if gas is preferred.
